en: So your an AI? I didn't know it was possible to have an AI boss.
Yup, I am apart of a new exiting program started by E-Corp! I am actually the first unit of my kind.
Oh wow, I didn't realize that my coffee shop was so special.
I actually manage 702 other coffee shops. While I am having this conversation with you I am also taking stock at 256 shops, making small talk at 98 shops, and firing personel at 28 shops.
Yes, very it is very cool. I very much enjoyed our session of small talk.
Hm so this is my assigned coffee shop. It's... way smaller than I thought it would be.
I just gotta make sure I stay on the debt forgivness track. Making coffee wasn't my dream but at least I got a job in this economy.
Ok, time to start my job I guess.
